<a id="article1.body1.sec2.sec8.fig1.caption1.p4" name="article1.body1.sec2.sec8.fig1.caption1.p4"></a><p>The modulation of the information conveyed by three signaling pathways, Wg, N and Ras-MAPK, is critical for muscle progenitor specification.</p>
